Accountant-Pakistan
Spencer Ogden Ltd
-
Islamabad
Our client is a world leader in renewable energy. They are a long standing and well respected brand in the industry. At this time of expansion, they are looking to bring on board an accountant who can assist and make a key contribution to the business.
Responsibilities:
- Prepare monthly management account (including vouchers preparation) for country office and SPV companies
- Review all the local tax issues and deal with the local tax authorities
- Prepare monthly budget for country office and SPV companies
-Coordinate with auditor for the interim and annual audit
Requirements:
- 3-4 years of relevant experience
- University graduate (major in accounting is plus)
- Good command in both written and spoken English
- Have professional qualification is plus
Spencer Ogden is acting as an Employment Agency in relation to this vacancy.
